Class DataSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.nofuturecorp.www.connector.DataSet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Iterable<ColumnSet>

    public class DataSet
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<ColumnSet>, java.io.Serializable
    Class to store the extracted rows of a query. The elements can be extracted from various different ways, similar to a list but also as a cursor (like an Android) or other iterable elements
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Juan José Longoria López
